  Khun-hong ti7 Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 in tau bak8-chit8-nih soa3 toa3 5, 6 jit8, in-ui7 in chin hoaN-hi2 i tiam3 leh. Khun-hong tiam3 liau2 ia7 chin u7 chhu3-bi7, in-ui7 u7 Hui7-bi2 thang choe3 phoaN7 kong2 oe7. In ia7 chin sin3-iong7 i, sou2-i2 in nng7 e5 chheng-lian5 tiaN7 chhoa7-chhut chhoa7-jip8. U7 si5 khi3 soaN-nih ban2 pek-hap8-hoe. U7-si5 khi3 khe-a2 tio3-hi5, oan2-ju5 hiaN moai7 e5 chhin-bit8. Tan7-si7 in nng7-lang5 e5 sim-keng2 bo5 tu2-tu2 siang7-khoan2. Chit8 e5 si7 teh siuN7 khah-hng7 khah-chhim e5 tai7-chi3, si7 iu2-i3-tek e5 kau-poe5. Chit8 e5 si7 ui7 su-liam7 ko-ko, si7 sun5-kiat e5 iu2-gi5 na7-tiaN7. Pai3 6 lah, Khun-hong chiu7 siuN7 beh to3-khi3 chiu7 kap in saN-si5. Bo5 phah-sng3 Lim5 TiuN2-lo2-niu5 soa3 koh siuN7 khi2 Teng-liong5 lai5 pi-siong, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni tai7-ke soa3 koh kiong5 lau5 i bin5-a2-jit8 tai7-ke thang choe3-hoe2 khi3 le2-pai3. Khun-hong khoaN3 in e5 chhin-chhiat, chiu7 koh tiam3 leh. Bin5-a2-jit8 tai7-ke chiu7 chhoa7-chhoa7 khi3 le2-pai3. Nng7 hiaN-so2 sio2-kou hu7-tam ka3 Iu3-ti7-kho. A-so2 toaN5 khim5, Hui7-bi2 chhoa7 hak8-seng iu5-hi3 chhiuN3-koa. Bo5 chit8-hang7 bo5 m7 chhim-chhim in2-khi2 Khun-hong to-tai7 e5 chu3-i3 kap su-liam7. Le2-pai3 soah tai7-ke ui5 oa2 lai5 ka7 tiuN2-lo2-niu5 ai-siong an-ui3. Ki5-sit8 chiah e5 su7 si7 ke-thiN choe3 lau7-bu2 e5 lang5 e5 siong-sim, chit8-si5 tiuN2-lo2-niu5 sim-chong7 soa3 koh bo5 lat8 beh to2 loh8-khi3. Tai7-khai3 si7 lang5 ui5 siuN-che7, ia7 kong2 siuN-che7 oe7, koh chin siong-sim. Soat-mui5 kap Hui7-bi2 khoaN3 ma-mah bin7 tng2-sek tit8-tit8 beh be7-kou3-tit, kin2 ka7 i chhah jip8-khi3 Bok8-su e5 pang5 hioh-khun3. Au7-lai5 put-chi2 khah song2-khoai3 chiah hou7 Hui7-bi2 kap Khun-hong chit8 lang5 thiaN7 chit8 peng5, un5-un5-a2 kiaN5 to3-khi3. Pai3-tng5 ti7 ke-a2-thau5, Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 in chhu3 khah ti7 ke-a2-boe2, chiam2-jian5 u7 kui2-na7 pah-pou7 e5 hng7. Chit8 lang5 thiaN7 chit8-peng5 soa3 chhin-chhiuN7 chin-chiaN3 e5 hiaN-moai7 e5 kam2-kak. Lau7 tiuN2-lo2 kap sim-pu7 Soat-mui5 toe3 ti7 sin-pi