  Sou2-i2 goa2 chhiaN2 Khun-hong-ko chhim-siuN7. Goa2 siuN7 lan2 e5 chhin-bit8, kau3 ti7 iu2-gi5 e5 theng5-tou7 chiu7 ho2. Goa2 ia7 hoaN-hi2 li2 an-ui3 goa2 e5 pe7-bo2, sou2-i2 chhim-chhim ka7 li2 seh-sia7. 
  Khun-hong khoaN3 tioh8 Hui7-bi2 e5 tai7-hong, cheng-kiat it-hoat kam2-hok8. Soa3 kam2-kak beh ban2 sui2 e5 mui5-kai3 m7-si7 sui5-pian7 kho2-khi, u7 i lai7-lai7 e5 chhi3. M7-na7 m7-kaN2 siu7-khi3 soa3 it-hoat hian2-beng5 i e5 un-khun5, ho2-i3 lai5 kou-chiaN5 Hui7-bi2. Ti7 bu5-i3 e5 tiong-kan, hut-jian5 pho7 Hui7-bi2 lai5 chim--i. Hui7-bi2 chin siu7-khi3 chiu7 an2-ni khia7 khi2--lai5, tiam7-tiam7 oat to3-khi3. To3-khi3 kau3-chhu3 jip8-khi3 pang5-nih mng5 koaiN-leh, phak ti7 i peng5-si5 teh thak8-chheh sia2-ji7 e5 toh-a2 lau5 bak8-sai2. I e5 sim chin kan-khou2, ka-ti7 kiam2-tiam2 i e5 heng5-ui5, tai7-khai3 si7 tui3 siuN7 su-liam7 ko-ko, sim bo5-liau5 khang-hi, hut-jian5 tit-tioh8 iN7-seng3 lam5 peng5-iu2, chhin-chhiuN7 hiaN-ko e5 khoan2-sit, chiu7 soa3 sit-loh8 kin2-sin7, bo5 kheh-khi3 e5 heng5-tong7, phah-sng3 si7 tui3 an2-ni e5 siu7 gou7-hoe7. Kin-ni5 Hui7-bi2 si7 21 hoe3, Khun-hong si7 27 hoe3, tai7-ke boe7 chhoa7, boe7 ke3. Nng7 e5 chheng-lian5 choe3-hoe2, bo5 siu7 koan2-sok, hong2-hut bo5 gi5-gou7 e5 si5, chiu7 an-cheng5 chhin-chhiuN7 thiau-phi5 e5 chok-giat8 gin2-na2 thau chau2-jip8 khi3 sim-pang5-nih, ki3-jian5 hou7 i thau-chau2-jip8--khi3, chin-chiaN3 si7 oh-tit koaN2 chhut-khi3. Hui7-bi2 chhim-chhim thong3-hoe2 i ka-ti7 choe3 sin3 Chu2 e5 lu2-chu2, bo5 kau3-giah8 kin2-sin7 lai5 siu7 lam5 peng5-iu2 e5 gou7-hoe7. I ka-ti7 chu7-chek, ia7 kam2-kak siu7 chin toa7 e5 bu2-jiok8. 
  Khun-hong siu7 si-ai3 (ai3-cheng5 beh hou7--lang5) e5 ku7-choat8, chit8-si5 kam2-kak bu5-beng5-hoe2 toa7-toh8. M7-chai siu7-khi3 an2-choaN2, soa3 chu7-pou7 chu7-khi3 e5 khoan2-sit, khia7 tiam3 hia gang7-gang7 khoaN3 Hui7-bi2 chau2 loh8 soaN bo5 saN-si5 choe3 i khi3 e5 poe7-iaN2, hou7-chu. Ti7 thiaN3-e5 lai7-bin7 khoaN3 sim2-mih8, thiaN sim2-mih8 to sui2. Chit8-sim khi3 Hui7-bi2 choe3 i khi3, chit8-sim soa3 kam2-poe7 Hui7-bi2 e5 jin5-keh e5 ko-kiat, u7 chi3-khi3. Tui3 pe7-bu2 iu2-hau3, tui3 chong-kau3 tiong-sit8. Tui3 iu2-gi5-ai3, kap loan5-ai3 u7 hun-beng5, sin5-seng3 put-kho2 chhim-hoan7. SiuN7-lai5 siuN7-khi3, koh si7 lai5 lang5-tau choe3 lang5-kheh, soa3 m7-kaN2 siu7-khi3. Chong2-si7 chin pai7-heng3, chin sit-i3, ka-ti7 chit8 e5 bo5-liau5 bo5-liau5 tui3 soaN-teng2 un5-un5-a2 tong7 loh8--lai5. Soa3 bo5 ban2 hoe, pun2 si7 siuN7 ban2 tam7-poh8 to3-khi3 thang sang3 peng5-iu2, taN lian7 tha-tu2-a2 ti7 lou7-nih beh lai5 kap Hui7-bi2 choe3-hoe2 ban2 e5 kui2-lui2-a2 ia7 thiah-thiah phaiN2 hiat-kak8 tiam3 lou7-piN. To3-khi3 kau3 Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 tau chin bo5-i3. So5-khi3 kheh-thiaN ka-ti7 chit8 e5 tiam7-tiam7 che7, chin phaiN2-se3 theh8 sin-bun5 om-bin7, na2-chun2 khun3-khi3 e5 khoan2-sit. 
  Hit-am3 chiah8-png7 Hui7-bi2 ia7 kak-tit chin phaiN2-se3, in-ui7 tui3 lai5 lan2-tau e5 lang5-kheh, hiah ho2-i3 ka7 lang5 lau5, ku7-choat8 e5 si5 m7 chai piau2-ian2 liau2 e7 siuN koe3 hoe2 a2-be7? M7-ku2 si7 chhut tui3 bu5-sia5 thian-chin e5 pun2-sim. Sim ka-ti7 chu7-sin3 si7 tioh8. In-ui7 sun5-kiat, cheng3-keng tek-khak m7-thang kap siok8-hoa3, chha-put-to, ma2-ma2 hu-hu saN hun7-chap8. Chong2-si7 lang5-kheh iau2 ti7 lan2 tau, ia7-si7 ai3 piau2-si7 ho2-i3. Khun-hong khoaN3 Hui7-bi2 ti7 chiah8 am3-tng3 peng5-jian5 piau2-si7 ho2-i3, chiu7 chin siu7 an-ui3. Keh chai2-khi2 chiu7 saN-si5 to3-khi3. An2-ni thau5-boe2 tiam3 Lim5 tiuN2-lo2-tau oa2 chiaN5-chap8-jit8. Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 chit8 ke ia7 ko2-jian5 toa7-toa5 siu7 an-ui3. 
  Kong2 Khun-hong to-si7 toa7-oh8 pit8-giap8, koh siong-tong e5 ka-teng5. Ka-ti7 su7-giap8 ia7 seng5-kong, an2-choaN2 e7 kau3 27 hoe3 iau2-boe7 chhoa7, che si7 chit8 e5 chin-chhim e5 goan5-in, bo5 kong2 lin2 long2 m7-chai. Goan5-in si7 Khun-hong e5 lau7-pe7 cha2-si5 choe3 koaN se3-ka-te2, na7-si7 kho2-sioh cha2-si2. Lau7-bu2 si7 chit8 e5 bu2-koaN chin u7 se3-lek8 e5 chiong-kun thoan5-tiuN2 e5 sio2-moai7. Tiong7-hu si2 liau2 chiu7 chiuN2 chheng-koaN2, chi2-u7 chiuN2 chit-e5 Khun-hong, si7 kim--e5, gin5--e5, po2-poe3 ni-ni, na2-chun2 ou7-hioh8 phang5 chin-chu lai5 chiuN2 chit e5 kiaN2. Ia7 chu7-se3 ui7 Khun-hong io chit8 e5 sim-pu7-a2. M7-si7 ui7 bo5 chiN5 lai5 io, si7 ui7 ai3 u7 phoaN7, ai3 chit8 tui3 kiaN2 khah nau7-jiat8. Chit e5 sim-pu7-a2 ia7-si7 siong-tong e5 mng5-hong e5 chhian-kim, tai7-ke si7 se3-kau e5 peng5-iu2. Kau3 toa7-han3 ia7 u7 khi3 thak8 lu2-chu2 ko-tiong. SeN-choe3 ia7-si7 chin sui2, chin u7 ta-ke-ian5. Chhut-si3 chiu7-si7 pai3-put8-a2 lang5, ta-ke si7 jiat8-sim e5 chhai3-kou, sou2-i2 kin-sui5 ta-ke sio-hiuN liam7-keng, pai3-put8 tak8-hang7 to chin koan3-si3. Chhai3-iu2 lai5-ong2 ia7 e7-chu2 chhai3-toh. Siong5-siong5 kin ta-ke khi3 sui5-hiuN. Ni5-cheh chhoe-koe2 pak8-chang3, hau3 mng5-khau2, pan7 seng-le2, tian7-chiu2, poah8-poe ku3 li2 kong2 kiaN7-kiaN7 to e7. It-hoat tit ta-ke thiaN3. Kin-ni5 26 hoe3 lah, chu7 kui2-na7-ni5 cheng5 in ta-ke chiu7 beh ka7 i choe3 toa7-lang5, na7-si7 m7-chai an2-choaN2 e7 bo5 Khun-hong e5 ian5. Sim-pu7-a2 e5 mia5 seN3 Li2 mia5 Siu3-chhun, khi3 hou7 khoaN3-mia7-e5 khoaN3, ka7 i thiah ji7-sou3 kong2 “Li2”, Li2 si7 li2-a2, tho5-li2 put-gian5 ha7 chu7 seng5 ke , i3-su3 si7 kong2 tho5-a2, li2-a2 kau3 si5 na7 sek8 m7-bian2 hou-kio3, lang5 chu7-jian5 e7 lai5 chhin-kin7, e7-bin7 bo5 lou7 ia7 e7 piN3 u7 lou7. “Siu3” si7 siu3-khi3, chhut-lui7 poat8-chui7, tok8-chhut bo5 lang5 e7-tit kap i pi2 ui5-chi “Siu3.” “Chhun” si7 chhun-thiN, ban7-but8 to hian2-chhut eng5-hian2, puh-ge5 thou3-iN2 bou7-seng7, chhun ni5-ni5 chhun, ban7-lian